## Validation Checklist

Before creating or renaming blog files, ensure:

- [ ] **Lowercase only:** No uppercase letters anywhere
- [ ] **Hyphen separation:** Words separated by hyphens (`-`)
- [ ] **No special characters:** Only letters, numbers, hyphens, and dots
- [ ] **Proper extension:** `.md`, `.us.md`, or `.es.md`
- [ ] **Descriptive slug:** Clearly indicates article content
- [ ] **Translation consistency:** Paired files have identical base names
- [ ] **Length appropriate:** Not too long (under 60 characters total)

